	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65137007"><p>Agile has some good aspects and some bad aspects.  It works better in some environments than it does in other environments.  And it can suffer from low competence or low buy-in from those attempting it.</p><p>People who have had a bad experience with it are going to hate it, and people who have had a good experience with it are going to like it.</p><p>So, there's my opinion of it.  I won't distill it down to a single "good" or "bad" because that would be a silly oversimplification.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_65137007">

